---
import WaveformPlayer from "./WaveformPlayer.astro";
import { site } from "../data/site";
---

<article class="call-card" aria-label="Демо обаждане към Vdiga">
  <div class="phone-top">
    <span></span>
    <strong>Входящ разговор</strong>
    <span class="live-dot">на линия</span>
  </div>
  <div class="call-card-inner">
    <p class="eyebrow compact">AI рецепционист</p>
    {
      site.demoPhone ? (
        <a class="demo-number" href={`tel:${site.demoPhone}`}>{site.demoPhone}</a>
      ) : (
        <strong class="demo-number muted-number">Демо поток</strong>
      )
    }
    <p class="card-copy">Клиент звъни, Vdiga пита за услугата, намира слот и връща кратко резюме към екипа.</p>
    <div class="button-row card-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/demo">Чуйте демото</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost-light" href="/kak-raboti">Как работи</a>
    </div>
    <ul class="call-meta">
      <li>24/7 отговор</li>
      <li>записване на час</li>
      <li>обобщение след разговор</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <WaveformPlayer />
</article>
